node.text:
【🏆 #9GagHomeOlympics TikTok Campaign 🏆】
-
Now that it’s officially The Olympics Season, we’d like to invite you all to take part in our #9GagHomeOlympics TikTok Campaign 🏠🏋🏻‍♂️
-
🏅Show the world what you got like an Olympian🏅
All you have to do is:
1. Create any funny at-home videos that show off your talents,
2. Upload your videos to TikTok with our #9GagHomeOlympics hashtag 💪
3. Follow @9GAG TikTok account 👉🏻  https://9g.ag/tiktok
-
The best ones will be shared on @9GAG’s Instagram and TikTok 👏 We can’t wait to see your work!
-
🎥 by @andriragettli
